title: SEASON REWARD
body: Hey i was place in gold 5 this season and i was wonering when will i get my skin? and will it include maokai as well? thanks for the feedback,

replies.body: Rewards are aimed to roll out in two weeks, per the [2016 Season](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon) guide.  Hang tight until then, and congratulations on making it to Gold!
